Dennis Chun https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dennis_Chun 0 Dennis Chun (born March 18, 1952) is an American actor, he is the son of actor Kam Fong Chun, and has a main role as Sgt. Duke Lukela in the 2010 remake of the 1968 television series Hawaii Five-O in which his father had a main role as Chin Ho Kelly.
